title: What are the best fictional band names? - Quora

response.answer_text: Considering that concocting band-names and pondering memes are the bulk of base thoughts that pass through my mind, I'm a veritable library of fictional band names! My girlfriend and I are always joking about how “Such-and-such would make a great band name!” it never stops—anywhere! In the car, at the table…in bed, even! Of course, this list will expand as I think of more: Supine and Fecund Cheddar Man & the Cannibals The Wonky Heathens Letting Dead Dogs Lie Three-Finger Vampire Death Stratified Squamous Bondage Tuxedo Sexless Hydrogen Synthetic Loofah Hollow Beginning we're trying to be edgy.
